## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [CS67234]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;epinastic cotyledons, long hypocotyls, curled rosette leaves, increased apical dominance, tall inflorescences, twisted cauline leaves, enlarged seeds. All phenotypes are caused by a gain-of-function yucca6-1D mutation
